{"tid":1589774,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國果邊啲支持就嚟一舖清袋","createTime":"2019-09-23T12:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T17:29:57.000Z","uid":315876,"like":53,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5ceaa09cf2bcbcec44839d9621755c83fbb2614d","tid":1589774,"uid":315876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:07:54.000Z","msg":"最近韓國演員金義聖好熱心咁想了解最近香港發生嘅事，幫我們喺韓國做咗好好的宣傳。但近排聽返嚟話有個會去韓國旅行嘅香港人認頭咗做29/9全球集會嘅首爾部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手唔係唔好，不過唔熟悉當地政治環境真係好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />竟然同緊當地反中反文在寅的右派政黨(你當係民賤聯啦，佢地支持貪污朴槿惠)聯絡，正正就係韓國民主人士年輕人最唔鐘意個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n住韓國果班香港人都唔贊成香港都無大台，個香港旅客就走去搵政黨，好明顯俾人利用咗去做當地藍絲都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者第日有韓國傳媒訪問點解同藍絲合作，要搵人follow up佢又返咗香港都唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1999 so99y"},{"pid":"5baa29893dee0cd06f5545714d411337e56ed3e7","tid":1589774,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"d95b9856a5d0cbc7d7a5d7ba07cd45ebaf8044ef","tid":1589774,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>十一國殤 全民黑衣</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ishNdyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FishNdyx.jpg&h=21d2a745&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UTDkyyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F